        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Eu<lb break="no" n="3"/>dia<lb break="no" n="4"/>prac<lb break="no" n="5"/>tus </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Isi<lb break="no" n="2"/>di <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>reg</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ex <lb n="2"/>vo<lb break="no" n="3"/>to </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschrift ist durch zwei Fußabdrücke in drei Kolumnen gegliedert; Votivformel steht unten waagerecht. (B): Wagner: Schlußzeile: O (klein) // I // m(onumentum) p(osuit) (mit Vorbehalt). Grimm: Schlußzeile: l(ibens) m(erito). SIRIS: Schlußzeile: I / MP. Bricault: Fehlender Zeilenfall Eu/dia. Material: Laaser Marmor.</p>
            </div>
